Only *new* features/bugfixes relative to python devchat-gui 1.30:

Fix:
    - 14 jun 2010: fubard greenie pseudohtml breaks chat
    - Session reinitialisation after long timeouts, e.g. due to standby/network down (I hate you, eduroam). Probably reopen main site?

New:
    - user definable shortcuts
    - multiple color schemes (Tango [light], Yaki [medium], Oblivion [dark], Egosoft, native), replace chat stock colors (red, cyan, yellow, chatname_green, etc.)
    - ignore list, levelfilter (tag every message with username, userlevel and chatlevel)
    - OTR encryption
    - save userlist width
    - sensible userlist size calculation on resize
    - Option to deactivate sending raw html for greenies (active by default)


